headline: Why Idexx Labs Stock Rocketed Higher This Week
summary: Shares of leading pet healthcare diagnostics provider Idexx Laboratories (NASDAQ: IDXX) were up by 9% this week as of 4 p.m. ET Thursday, according to data provided by S&P Global Market Intelligence.  Idexx Labs reported fourth-quarter earnings Monday morning that surpassed analysts' expectations for revenue and earnings per share (EPS).  After pulling forward growth during the pandemic, the veterinary industry has yet to return to normal, making Idexx's Q4 results and guidance reassuring for investors.
